snippet.textDisplay: when farheen was talking about the situations where we don't know what's ahead, i felt that. shivers went through my body because that's exactly what im going through, it's so uncertain and i cant see the light ahead of me. it makes you anxious and impatient and it eats you from the inside. this was needed, those words from someone like farheen were needed who has been going through the same. things like this make you believe in something that your heart doesn't want you to believe in, because of the hardships and obstacles that are on the way of the whole process. thank you coke studio, all these songs have been speaking to my heart and somehow making me feel better every time i feel low or hopeless. thank you to farheen and specially sajjad bhai for explaining me and million others like me that everything will be fine, der se hi sahi but we'll all make it, we'll all see the light at the end of the tunnel ❤️‍🩹

snippet.textDisplay: I'm just speechless...looking at this BTS has literally sent shivers inside me. This song is so soothing, melodious, meaningful, and it hits differently. And what to say about "CHIEF SAHAB" Sajjad Ali, I grew up listening to him, and there are very few people in this world who have properly handled the fame, the glamour, and the buzz around them, and Sajjad Ali is definitely one those people who handled everything such gracefully, remained very down-to-earth throughout his career, gave respect to everybody around him, and in return earned immense respect. He still remains the talk of the town even after so many decades, and this is his greatest achievement. I think Farheen should have sung a bit more, that is the only lacking I can point out as far this song is concerned. But overall it's a fabulous soul-touching song without a doubt. Thank you COKE STUDIO Pakistan for pressing the right cords inside us and bringing out our sorrows and joys, and making us think deeply about our lives. COKE STUDIO! I love you from the bottom of my heart, keep up the excellent work, and please continue to shake our souls!♥♥♥♥♥♥
